data.description:
El Dorado Springs Country Home For Sale
For Sale just minutes from El Dorado Springs is a unique country home that deserves your attention. With almost 2900 sq feet this home has tons of space and tons of possibilities. This home naturally divides into 2 quarters that can be closed for privacy or open for easy natural flow. The home has 2 living areas; 2 kitchen/dining areas; 2 laundry rooms; separate front and back doors; & zoned heating and cooling with 2 units. The home has 5 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and is handicap accessible including a full-sized walk-in shower in one bathroom and a walk-in tub in the other bathroom.  Rooms throughout the home are spacious and 2 of the bedrooms have huge walk-in closets. The home sits on 1.4 secluded acres with a 30x40’ detached garage/shop with concrete floor and electric. An additional detached garage provides more storage and parking.  Schedule to see it to fully appreciate what this home has to offer.
